Body: WOLK TOKEN IS NOW LIVE!   Introducing Wolk, a blockchain-based advertising data exchange, powered by the WOLK token. Created by experts and data scientists with decades of experience in digital advertising and performance-based marketing.  More information at  http://www.wolk.com   Check out our Video https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sWzRN5U-Y5o&t=0s   Join Us on Reddit https://www.reddit.com/r/wolktoken  The vision of the company Wolks mission to create open data sharing systems for the world. We aim to decentralize and democratize access to the world's data.  The purpose of the technology The technology exists to make valuable data more accessible. Data is the world's most valuable resource. By decentralizing access to the richest data sets, there is no limit on how humanity can grow and improve.  The problem it aims to solve Currently, the world's most powerful data sets sit locked behind walled gardens. Data needs to be unlocked in a way that honors individuals needs for privacy, of course.   The Wolk Protocol defines how data buyers and suppliers use decentralized virtual currencies (WOLK token) with APIs (Wolk API) to transact using decentralized backend storage.    * Presale is now Live Started at September 10, 2017 23:00  * WOLK Token Generation Event is:     Start Time: September 18, 2017 23:00 GMT (Block 4289200)     End Time: October 9 - 12, 2017 (Block 437000)

Body: I get some of those tokens too. I am not sure if that tokens are actual useable or just some throw in ad-tokens you only get, when you actually participate in the ICO like e.g. Cryptonex did it. I am personally not a fan of this new wave of "free" tokens that appear in my wallet. It just feels like the ads, I get in my mailbox. Furthermore it does make the project look kind of shady / scammy do be honest.  I know "free" coins are great and all ... but let's be honest... it is not like that this free coins you got, will be ever worth several 1000 bucks, like BTC. In my opinion, it is just a new annoying way to advertise an ICO.
